B2R2

Opcode Type

Namespace: B2R2.FrontEnd.BinLifter.Intel
Assembly: B2R2.FrontEnd.BinLifter.Intel.dll
Base Type: Enum
All Interfaces: IComparable , IConvertible , IFormattable
Kind: Struct
This is an enum type definition

Intel opcodes. This type should be generated using scripts/genOpcode.fsx from the `IntelSupportedOpcodes.txt` file.
